{"tid":1844744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個膠鐵站真係唔拆唔撚得","createTime":"2020-01-26T18:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T19:07:17.000Z","uid":127333,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"85a84b51552c8ed210c3d3f408df658d6552debc","tid":1844744,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGe6aJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGe6aJr.png&h=12cdaf17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個濕鳩膠鐵係無撚用<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無撚用</span></span>呀<br />\n屌你老母放啲大陸喱落黎害撚死香港<br />\n班垃圾膠官唔撚停呀嘛<br />\n我地幫佢停 搵日就拆撚咗佢舊垃圾<br />\n一把火燒撚咗個一地兩檢關口<br />\n成個站燒毒啦屌你老母<br />\n我話撚知佢放一百個防暴係入邊定點<br />\n我地就圍撚住個濕鳩站黎燒 <br />\n幫你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">高溫燒毒</span></span>呀柒頭"},{"pid":"a1ba2d198ef9d0f496b0765117f11afbd21a86ab","tid":1844744,"uid":28028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:47:21.000Z","msg":"叫毒鐡"},{"pid":"354ecf123b24d4780bd65597a1d2e416efbc39bc","tid":1844744,"uid":127333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:48:16.000Z","msg":"無撚用既野就拆撚咗佢啦屌<br />\n上水啲濕鳩關口仲唔撚夠呀？<br />\n係要整個快速傳染通道比啲濕鳩大陸喱落黎傳播病毒<br />\n拆撚咗佢啦 叫班柒頭行撚開啦<br />\n防暴要守就守撚飽佢 攬撚住個忠誠勇毅支旗仔同啲武漢肺炎大陸柒頭去死啦"},{"pid":"06ef963bb065b626c3848ff7182489799d1bc992","tid":1844744,"uid":31317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"錯過左時機，之後肯定重兵<br />\n仲要蝗蟲有名你叫蝗蟲，真係無孔不入，<br />\n太多窿路根本無法堵截。"},{"pid":"dc25a91132f04a827b51c41f0bbe598529f1929c","tid":1844744,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:49:48.000Z","msg":"其實真係要搵日黃藍合作燒撚左個膠鐵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc3c80af6a7092756026210612509ee90b2e824","tid":1844744,"uid":78769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:49:52.000Z","msg":"一早已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年我哋冇有效地抗爭"},{"pid":"17ce465fafed27212b9f27e4ad20944d8564fb7a","tid":1844744,"uid":92082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"手足自行封關，絕對係唯一方法"},{"pid":"ec921f0f57f0684c5cd5397b46abed1d0e233791","tid":1844744,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ef963bb065b626c3848ff7182489799d1bc992","tid":1844744,"uid":31317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"錯過左時機，之後肯定重兵<br />\n仲要蝗蟲有名你叫蝗蟲，真係無孔不入，<br />\n太多窿路根本無法堵截。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母係都要we connect<br />\nCon佢老母呀<br />\n林鄭月娥條仆街臭閪係要做毒后<br />\n係要放啲大陸超級傳播者落黎<br />\n燒撚咗個膠鐵站佢<br />\n再燒撚埋啲垃圾關口<br />\n依家教個政府點撚樣治本呀 <br />\n話搵唔撚到源頭 個源頭咪係支那人的存在囉"},{"pid":"c7567a8ece994f6f555651a8e69e832357f2a40c","tid":1844744,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:57:16.000Z","msg":"政府真係戇鳩鳩<br />\n學校都有教你垃圾係可以焚化解決啦<br />\n再唔係咪源頭減廢 cut撚哂啲關口佢囉<br />\n屌係要放啲垃圾落黎<br />\n之前就搶我啲屋 搶我啲綜援 搶我啲奶粉<br />\n而家搶我啲口罩 搶我啲床位 <br />\n你個臭閪政府仲同我講一家人？<br />\n我屌你老母呀踢鳩柒佢地走啦"},{"pid":"decf8fcd0bc00575887fb9c8189c638cdeda7d92","tid":1844744,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9LhhtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9LhhtW.png&h=6359a7be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOwPS2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOwPS2g.jpg&h=18856b97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"133a6c82a82e15476714e5f39a4a38c85a971b7a","tid":1844744,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"decf8fcd0bc00575887fb9c8189c638cdeda7d92","tid":1844744,"uid":303052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T18:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9LhhtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn